
<div class="start-screen">
	<div class="logo">
		@@include('logo.svg')
	</div>
	<div class="byline">
		<p>By <a href="https://pudding.cool/author/matt-daniels/">Matt Daniels</a></p>
	</div>
	<div class="mountain">
		<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="56" height="27" viewBox="0 0 56 27" fill="none">
			<path d="M0 26H10.1887L13.3019 20.383L16.4151 24L22.3585 12.2766L28.3019 23L41.6038 2L54.9057 26" stroke="url(#paint0_linear)" stroke-width="2"/>
			<defs>
				<linearGradient id="paint0_linear" x1="27.4528" y1="-2" x2="27.4528" y2="26" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
					<stop stop-color="#16276A"/>
					<stop offset="0.359116" stop-color="#0C9275"/>
					<stop offset="1" stop-color="#EEE6D2"/>
				</linearGradient>
			</defs>
		</svg>
	</div>
	<p class="big-text">Human Terrain</p>
	<p class="sub-text">Visualizing the world’s Population, in 3D</p>
	<div class="prose">
		<p>Kinshasa, DRC is now bigger than Paris.  Guangzhou, Hong Kong, and Shenzhen are  forming an epic, 40 million-person super city.</p>
		<p>Over the past 30 years, the scale of population change is hard to grasp. How do you even visualize 10 million people?</p>
	</div>
	<div class="start-button">
		<p>Loading...</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="top-header">
	<a href='https://pudding.cool' target='_blank' class='logo'>
		@@include('logo.svg')
	</a>
	<div class="top-toggles">
		<div id="compare-button"><p>Compare to 1990</p></div>
		<div id="present-button"><p class="top-toggle-active">Population Present Day</p></div>
		<div id="delta-button"><p>Change, 1990-2015</p></div>
	</div>
	<div class="population">
		<p>100 million people</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="screen">

</div>


<div class="map-container">
	<div class="before-map-container">
		<div class="before-toggles">
			<div class="before-present-toggles">
				<p class="before-present-toggle before-toggle-active">2015</p>
			</div>
			<div class="before-historic-toggles">
				<p class="before-historic-toggle before-toggle-active">1990</p>
				<p class="before-historic-toggle">1975</p>
				<p class="before-historic-toggle">2000</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id='compare-map' class='map'></div>
	</div>
	<div id='main-map' class='map'></div>
	<div class="delta-map-container">
		<div id='delta-map' class="map">
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="toggles">

</div>

<div class="delta-map-container">
	<div class="delta-map">

	</div>
</div>

<div class="tour-container tour-hidden tour-hidden-start">
	<div class="tour-hide">
		<div class="tour-hide-arrow">
			<div>@@include('chevron-down.svg')</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tour-show-arrow">
			<div>@@include('chevron-up.svg')</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="tour-text-container">
		<p class="tour-text">Something about world cities.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="tour-button">Fly to Kinshasa
	</div>
	<div class="tour-toggle">
		<div class="tour-toggle-left">
			<div>@@include('chevron-left.svg')</div>
		</div>
		<div class="tour-toggle-text">
			<p class="tour-toggle-text-current">1
			</p>
			<p class="tour-toggle-text-amount">of 21
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="tour-toggle-right">
			<div>@@include('chevron-right.svg')</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
